---
// File: src/pages/method.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Method | Stacksolver UK"
  description="How Stacksolver UK delivers bespoke enterprise systems: discovery, design, delivery and continuous support — with governance built in from day one."
>
  <section class="min-h-screen flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-24">
      <p class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-olive-600 dark:text-olive-400 mb-6">Method</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-8">
        Discovery. Design. Delivery. Support.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-12">
        Every engagement follows the same four-stage cadence. Each stage produces a tangible artefact
        and a clear go / no-go decision before the next stage begins.
      </p>
      <ol class="space-y-6">
        <li class="flex gap-5">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-olive-500 text-zinc-900 font-bold flex items-center justify-center">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Discovery</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Understand current state, regulatory constraints and business objectives. Output: scoping memo and prioritised roadmap.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-5">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-olive-500 text-zinc-900 font-bold flex items-center justify-center">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Design</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Solution architecture, data model, security controls and integration points — agreed with your stakeholders before a single line of code is written.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-5">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-olive-500 text-zinc-900 font-bold flex items-center justify-center">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Delivery</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Iterative build with weekly demos, structured user acceptance testing and a documented handover.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-5">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-olive-500 text-zinc-900 font-bold flex items-center justify-center">4</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Support</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Ongoing retainer covering enhancements, compliance updates and operational support.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500 italic pt-12 mt-12 border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
        A detailed methodology page with case studies and downloadable framework is being prepared.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-olive-500 text-zinc-900 font-semibold border border-olive-500 hover:bg-olive-600 transition-colors">
          Discuss your project <span aria-hidden>→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
